org.springframework.web.servlet.view.tiles3

类 SpringLocaleResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.tiles.locale.impl.DefaultLocaleResolver
      • org.springframework.web.servlet.view.tiles3.SpringLocaleResolver
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    LocaleResolver

    public class SpringLocaleResolver
extends DefaultLocaleResolver
    Tiles LocaleResolver adapter that delegates to a Spring LocaleResolver, exposing the DispatcherServlet-managed locale.

    This adapter gets automatically registered by TilesConfigurer.

    从以下版本开始:
    3.2
    作者:
    Nicolas Le Bas
